# HN Dashboard (Hello Neighbor operations)

Next.js 14 Pages Router app on Cloudflare (OpenNext). Supabase Postgres backend.

## Layout

- `pages/` — routes; API handlers in `pages/api/`
- `components/` — React UI
- `lib/` — shared utilities, auth, integrations
- `supabase/migrations/` — schema changes
- `docs/` — AUTH, CLOUDFLARE, BOOKKEEPING

## Integrations

- **Supabase** — `lib/db.js`
- **Plaid** — bank feed (`lib/plaid.js`, `pages/api/bank/`)
- **Hospitable** — reservations (`lib/hospitable.js`)
- **In-app forms** — turn clean checklist (`lib/forms/`, `pages/forms/`)

## Auth & roles

Session auth via iron-session (`lib/auth.js`). Admin vs cleaner roles in `lib/roles.js` — see `docs/AUTH.md`.

## Commands

- `npm run dev` — local dev
- `npm run deploy:cloudflare` — production deploy
- `npm run db:check` — verify Supabase connection

## Conventions

- JavaScript throughout (not TypeScript)
- Minimal diffs; match existing patterns in `lib/` and sibling components
- Do not commit unless asked
